---
import CampaignLayout from '../../layouts/CampaignLayout.astro';
---

<CampaignLayout
  title="Solidarity with Katie | Level Up"
  description="Katie is facing trial for ending a pregnancy. Show your solidarity and stand with women prosecuted under Britain's archaic abortion laws."
  heroImage="https://welevelup.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Screenshot-2024-06-14-at-12-1.webp"
  heroTitle="Solidarity with Katie"
>

  <h1 class="campaign-main-title">Solidarity with Katie</h1>

  <div class="campaign-section">
    <div class="campaign-section__label" style="width: 100%; max-width: 100%;">
      &nbsp;
    </div>
    <div class="campaign-section__text">
      <p>Katie* is facing trial for ending a pregnancy, and is living with the stress and trauma of an ongoing police investigation into her NHS-prescribed abortion. This is all due to an outdated law from 1861 that makes abortion a criminal offence.</p>
      <p>Abortion is healthcare, and should be treated as such. This is why Level Up is campaigning for the outdated 1861 law to be removed, and abortion to be decriminalised. Until we achieve that, <strong>the most important thing we can do is show solidarity with women who are still being prosecuted under these archaic laws.</strong></p>
      <p>It's crucial that Katie knows the public are on her side – please share a message of support, and we will pass them onto Katie.</p>
      <p><em>* Katie is not her real name.</em></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="campaign-block campaign-block--navy">
    <p class="campaign-block__heading">Messages of solidarity</p>
    <div class="campaign-block__text">
      <p>Hundreds of people from the Level Up community have sent messages of support to Katie. Each message is an act of solidarity against criminalisation.</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
        <a href="https://levelup.yourmovement.org/p/join-us" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="campaign-btn">Join the Level Up Community</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="campaign-section">
    <div class="campaign-section__label">
      <h2>Why this matters</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="campaign-section__text">
      <p>Britain's abortion law is still governed by the Offences Against the Person Act 1861 – a law passed over 160 years ago, before women had the right to vote. This law means that anyone who has an abortion outside of the legal framework can face criminal prosecution.</p>
      <p>Cases like Katie's show why decriminalisation is so urgently needed. No one should face prosecution for accessing healthcare.</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
        <a href="/campaigns/abortion-is-healthcare" class="campaign-btn">Support the Abortion is Healthcare Campaign</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

</CampaignLayout>
